Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.26,0:22:49.06,AitakuteRomaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}ima kimi wa doko ni iru no nani shite'ru no
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.77,0:22:58.61,AitakuteRomaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}kami{\fsp-2\fs40}- {\fsp\fs}sama ni negai todoku nara mou ichido dake
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.28,0:23:06.12,AitakuteRomaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}aitakute kimi ni aitakute
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.62,0:23:15.08,AitakuteRomaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}ima mo kono mune wa kimi{\fsp-2\fs40}- {\fsp\fs}iro ni somaru (dakishimetakute)
